Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promed@promedmail.org>

[It appears that the source of the outbreak strain of _S._ Paratyphi B, probably the d-tartrate fermenting variant _S. enterica_ subspecies _enterica_ serovar Paratyphi B dT+ (sometimes referred to as _S._ Java), has been identified as the starter culture. ProMED-mail awaits more information regarding the possibility of additional cultures in other states related to the same source.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/2iHP. - Mod. LL]
